      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;I'd like to gather some ideas on quantitative changes that could be made to PvP in general. These are things that should be simple, such as &amp;quot;change the base resist on spell X from Y to Z&amp;quot; or &amp;quot;raise the cap on A from B to C&amp;quot;. This is NOT a discussion about who owns who, or which class is the most overpowered, or what needs to be nerfed first, I just want to collect some easy balancing ideas after that point I will find a happy medium and see what comes out.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;EDIT for clarification: think of this as a thread for needed changes that can easily be done, put wants and wishes in the other thread.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Pinhedd_SZ on &lt;span class="date_text"&gt;01-27-2006&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="time_text"&gt;07:51 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
