      <title>My opinion on that top 10 list</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=PVP&amp;message.id=11510#M11510</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;1)         More people want to see that the people who train all the time and blatenly hack al the time get banned.  There are less MQ2/Showeq users on Zek than on any other server.  But the people who use it and use it all the time and nothing happens to them.  This problem can be fixxed easy.  Go to the big pvp battles annon and watch.  Everyone warping ban them right then and there.  Go to a few raids anon of the top guilds and see who uses the hax and ban them right there.  This will get rid of the top 10 known hackers on the server warning ppl that the developers are watching them and doing thier job.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2)        The resist on procs is not that major, and developers havent been looking at it for a long while.  Move it down the list to a lower number.   Most people who care about this are over powered melee who want to proc even more stuns.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3)         Points have meant nothing since day 1 it was implemented.  The turning in of Signets from Sullon Zek made it even more so.  The only real problem I see is that the gear you can buy needs to be updated to about time level gear instead of just VT gear.  Again not a major issue that the devs havent looked at.  Move it down the list.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4)         Out of range healers and buffers are plain stupid.  The best fix for this is if they heal or buff someone who is pvping they should lose thier status and become pvp enabled.  Again not a major issue, but if the level range was opened to +/- 20 levels pvp would open up and cause more action.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5)        Poor sks cant tap.  Help them out!  Other than potions its the only way they can heal themselves.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6)        Rangers are way over powered and thier shooting out thier rear while running oor makes them invincable to all casters.  Casters cant hit them unless they can see thier feet.  Why isnt bowing the same way.  Either make spells the same or fix rangers.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7)        Bards mana drain does suck.  Only problem is that there are not enough bards to make this a real problem. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;8)        Discord was fun, but only for a few days.  Fix this server before starting a new one.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;9)        Yes monks are over powered with thier chain stuns, but also look at run 8 and tstaff.  Make them resistable and have run 8 be reduced to run 5 on zek.  Run 8 was for pulling mobs, but now a monk can run from just inside my spell casting range with a 30% focus to melee range before i can get a 2.3 second cast spell off.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;10)      What is the point of spells being able to hit more if they dont land?  Both need to be fixed.  They should land for more and land more often.  Also since melee have such a distinct advantage in pvp, casters should get melee avoidance and mitagtion.&lt;/div&gt;</description>
